OL,3,CLabour and Tories have pledged not to
OL,4,Craise taxes - but do their plans add
OL,5,Cup?
OL,7,FBoth Labour and the Tories have
OL,8,Fpledged to get national debt falling
OL,9,Fif they win the election, and both
OL,10,Fparties have also told us they won't
OL,11,Fraise any of the major - NI, income
OL,12,Ftax and VAT - in the next parliament.
OL,14,FBut these pledges will be hard to keep.
OL,16,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies has
OL,17,Fcalculated the next government will
OL,18,Fhave to make between #30 and #40
OL,19,Fbillion of annual spending cuts.
